ACCORDING to Julius Malema, farmers have been approaching
banks to get money in exchange for their land.The leader of the EFF was speaking at the Standard Bank
Arena in Joburg during the party’s election registration campaign yesterday.Addressing EFF members in the packed arena, Malema said:
